<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>That isnt how the items work.  If you really want to know, goto the AllaKhazam sight and click on classes.  Then visit the links there.  One of them will explain how it works. Shovel and Earth - higher agi.  Stein and Water = the hp of the Earth.  Broom and Air = HP of the Water.  Torch and Fire = HP of an Air.  They are NOT higher lvl.  The items have no affect on level whatsoever.  Your pets have better stats is all.  Its like buffing them (but the buff stays until they die).  Summonned pets with it that appear to be higher is just luck.  At low lvls its very easy to get high pets.  At high lvls your pets will ALWAYS be blue(or worse) to you. </font></td></tr></table>
